Input.head: critic
Input.examplesent1: She felt she could not just be an armchair critic - it was her moral responsibility to do something.
Input.examplesent2: He will be quoted as an example of ' all that is wrong with the game ' by every armchair critic in Wales.
Input.examplesent3: I caught the train to get back home to be an armchair critic of England's football team performance against Jamaica.
